R and the tidyverse

R

An environment and a language for data analysis and programming

  • Free
  • Flexible
  • Powerful

R Growth

Rstudio

A powerful IDE for R.

The tidyverse

A collection of R packages for working with data in a common way.

Package installation

Extra functionality that can be added to R

install.packages("tidyverse") # Install the package
library(tidyverse) # Load the tidyverse

The tidyverse

  • ggplot2 - making graphs
  • dplyr - manipulating data
  • readr/readxl - getting data in to R
